values: {"display":"Parameters","filter":"[\"AMER\", \"EMEA\", \"APAC\", \"JP\", \"LACA\", \"Other\"]","level_1":"Region","level_2":"Country","level_3":"City","Master_l1":"Segment_Hierarchy","Master_l1_Rank":"Segment_Hierarchy_Rank","filter_REDACCOUNTS":"[\"Marketing Cloud\", \"Other\", \"Quip\", \"Sales Cloud\", \"Salesforce Platform\", \"Service Cloud\", \"Commerce Cloud\", \"Success Cloud\",\"Core Premier (A la Carte) & Priority\",\"Integration\"]","static_country_logic":"case when ('Region' == \"AMER\" && ('Country' ==  \"Canada\" )) then \"Canada\" when ('Region' == \"AMER\" && ('Country' ==  \"United States\" ))then \"United States\" when ('Region' == \"AMER\")then \"RO AMER\" when  ('Region' == \"EMEA\" && ('Country' ==  \"United Kingdom\" ))then \"United Kingdom\"  when  ('Region' == \"EMEA\" && ('Country' ==  \"France\" ))then \"France\" when ('Region' == \"EMEA\" && ('Country' ==  \"Germany\" ))then \"Germany\" when  ('Region' == \"EMEA\" && ('Country' ==  \"Netherlands\" ))then \"Netherlands\" when ('Region' == \"EMEA\" ) then \"RO EMEA\" when  ('Region' == \"APAC\" && ('Country' ==  \"Australia\" ))then \"ANZ\"  when  ('Region' == \"APAC\" && ('Country' ==  \"ANZ\" ))then \"ANZ\"when  ('Region' == \"APAC\" && ('Country' ==  \"India\" ))then \"India\"  when  ('Region' == \"APAC\" )then \"RO APAC\"  when  ('Region' == \"APAC\" )then \"RO APAC\"  when  ('Region' == \"JP\" && ('Country' ==  \"Japan\" ))then \"Japan\" when ('Region' == \"JP\" && ('Country' == \"South Korea\")) then \"South Korea\" when  ('Region' == \"JP\"  )then \"RO JP\"  when  ('Region' == \"LACA\" && ('Country' ==  \"Brazil\" ))then \"Brazil\" when ('Region' == \"LACA\" )then \"RO LACA\" when ('Region' == \"Other\" )then \"Other\" else \"ERROR\" end"}

Table_Level_2_Measures_4.label: Table_Level_2_Measures_4
Table_Level_2_Measures_4.query:
MasterHierarchy = load "Master_Hierarchy";
MasterHierarchy = filter MasterHierarchy by 'Level_1' in   {{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------LOAD/FILTER ACV------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ACV = load "APM_ACV_AUTO1";ACV = filter ACV by 'Segment' {{cell(Toggle_CSG_1.selection,0,"value").asString()}} "CSG";
ACV = filter ACV by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' in {{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};
ACV = group ACV by ('Quarter','Month', 'Fiscal_Year', 'Region' , 'Country');
ACV = foreach ACV generate  'Quarter' as 'Quarter', 'Fiscal_Year' as 'Fiscal_Year' ,'Month' as 'Month',sum('ACV') as 'ACV',"N/A" as 'City', 'Region' as 'Region',  {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"static_country_logic").asString()}} as 'Country' ;
q2_CYACV = filter ACV by 'Month' in  {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q2_PYACV = filter ACV by 'Month' in  {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_CYACV = filter ACV by 'Month' in  {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"YTD_Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_PYACV = filter ACV by 'Month' in  {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"YTD_Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};


----------------------------------------LOAD CSM------------------------------
CSM = load "CSM_PSM_HC";
CSM = filter CSM by 'Segment' {{cell(Toggle_CSG_2.selection,0,"value").asString()}} "CSG";
--CSM = filter CSM by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' in  {{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};
CSM = foreach CSM generate  'Cloud' as 'Cloud',"N/A" as 'City', 'Quarter' as 'Quarter', 'Fiscal_Year' as 'Fiscal_Year','Month' as 'Month' ,sum('CSM_Headcount') as 'CSM_Headcount', sum('PSM_Headcount') as 'PSM_Headcount','Region' as 'Region',{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"static_country_logic").asString()}} as 'Country';
q2_CYCSM = filter CSM by 'Quarter' in {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}} && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q2_PYCSM = filter CSM by 'Quarter' in {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}} && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q2_PY_2_CSM = filter CSM by 'Quarter' in {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}} && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY_2").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q3_CYCSM = filter CSM by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter_CSM").asString()}}) && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q3_PYCSM = filter CSM by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter_CSM").asString()}}) && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q3_PY_2_CSM = filter CSM by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter_CSM").asString()}}) && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY_2").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});

------------------------------------LOAD /FILTER RED ACCOUNTS---------------------------------------
REDACCOUNTS = load "APM_REDACCOUNTS";
REDACCOUNTS = filter REDACCOUNTS by 'Segment' {{cell(Toggle_CSG_2.selection,0,"value").asString()}} "CSG";
REDACCOUNTS = filter REDACCOUNTS by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' in  {{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};
REDACCOUNTS = foreach REDACCOUNTS generate 'Cloud' as 'Cloud', "N/A" as 'City', 'Quarter' as 'Quarter', 'Fiscal_Year' as 'Fiscal_Year','Month' as 'Month' ,sum('Red_Accounts') as 'Red_Accounts','Region' as 'Region',{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"static_country_logic").asString()}} as 'Country';
q2_CYREDACCOUNTS = filter REDACCOUNTS by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}}) && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q2_PYREDACCOUNTS = filter REDACCOUNTS by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Quarter").asString()}}) && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q3_CYREDACCOUNTS = filter REDACCOUNTS by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter").asString()}}) && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});
q3_PYREDACCOUNTS = filter REDACCOUNTS by ('Quarter' in {{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"YTD_Quarter").asString()}}) && ({{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}});


--------------------------------Grouping Level_1 -----------------------------------------
result =  group 
q2_CYACV by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
q2_PYACV by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
q3_CYACV by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
q3_PYACV by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
 

q2_CYCSM by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
q2_PYCSM by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full,
q2_PY_2_CSM by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
q3_CYCSM by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
q3_PYCSM by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
q3_PY_2_CSM by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 

q2_CYREDACCOUNTS by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
q2_PYREDACCOUNTS by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
q3_CYREDACCOUNTS by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
q3_PYREDACCOUNTS by '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' full, 
MasterHierarchy by 'Level_1';


------------------------PROJECTION LEVEL1-------------------------
result = foreach result generate 

" " + coalesce(MasterHierarchy.'Level_1', q2_CYACV.'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', q2_PYACV.'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', q3_CYACV.'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', q3_PYACV.'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', q2_CYREDACCOUNTS.'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', q2_PYREDACCOUNTS.'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', q3_CYREDACCOUNTS.'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', q3_PYREDACCOUNTS.'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}') as '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}',  

last(MasterHierarchy.'Level_1_Ranking') as 'Sort_Code',

coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} ACV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as 'YTD ACV Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} ACV Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD ACV Growth', 


coalesce(sum(q2_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Red_Accounts Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0) as 'YTD Red_Accounts Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Red_Accounts Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Red_Accounts Growth',

(coalesce(sum(q2_CYCSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0)) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM Absolute', 
(coalesce(sum(q3_CYCSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0))  as 'YTD CSM Absolute' ,  
((power(coalesce(sum(q2_CYCSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q2_PY_2_CSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100)  as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM CAGR',
((power(coalesce(sum(q3_CYCSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q3_PY_2_CSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100) as 'YTD CSM CAGR',

(coalesce(sum(q2_CYCSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0)) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM Absolute', 
(coalesce(sum(q3_CYCSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0))  as 'YTD PSM Absolute' ,  
((power(coalesce(sum(q2_CYCSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q2_PY_2_CSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM CAGR',
((power(coalesce(sum(q3_CYCSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q3_PY_2_CSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100) as 'YTD PSM CAGR';

-------------------------------------GROUPING Level_2------------------------------
result_SubCloud = group 
q2_CYACV by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 
q2_PYACV by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 
q3_CYACV by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 
q3_PYACV by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 


q2_CYCSM by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 
q2_PYCSM by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full,
q2_PY_2_CSM by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 
q3_CYCSM by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 
q3_PYCSM by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 
q3_PY_2_CSM by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 


q2_CYREDACCOUNTS by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 
q2_PYREDACCOUNTS by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 
q3_CYREDACCOUNTS by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 
q3_PYREDACCOUNTS by ('{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}') full, 

MasterHierarchy by ('Level_1', 'Level_2') ;


-------------------------------------PROJECTION Level_2------------------------------------
result_SubCloud = foreach result_SubCloud generate  

coalesce(q2_CYACV.'Country', q2_PYACV.'Country', q3_CYACV.'Country', q3_PYACV.'Country', q2_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Country', q2_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Country', q3_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Country', q3_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Country') as 'Country', 

coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} ACV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as 'YTD ACV Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} ACV Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD ACV Growth',

coalesce(sum(q3_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0) as 'YTD Red_Accounts Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Red_Accounts Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Red_Accounts'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Red_Accounts Growth',

(coalesce(sum(q2_CYCSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0)) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM Absolute', 
(coalesce(sum(q3_CYCSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0))  as 'YTD CSM Absolute' ,  
((power(coalesce(sum(q2_CYCSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q2_PY_2_CSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100)  as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM CAGR',
((power(coalesce(sum(q3_CYCSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q3_PY_2_CSM.'CSM_Headcount'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100) as 'YTD CSM CAGR',

(coalesce(sum(q2_CYCSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0)) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM Absolute', 
(coalesce(sum(q3_CYCSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0))  as 'YTD PSM Absolute' ,  
((power(coalesce(sum(q2_CYCSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q2_PY_2_CSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100)  as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM CAGR',
((power(coalesce(sum(q3_CYCSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0) / coalesce(sum(q3_PY_2_CSM.'PSM_Headcount'), 0),(1/2))-1)*100) as 'YTD PSM CAGR',

coalesce(MasterHierarchy.'Level_1' ,q2_CYACV.'Region', q2_PYACV.'Region', q3_CYACV.'Region', q3_PYACV.'Region', q2_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Region', q2_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Region', q3_CYREDACCOUNTS.'Region', q3_PYREDACCOUNTS.'Region') as 'Region_Level2';


-----------------------------------------Country Bin logic as data couldn't be provided in a clean format, this code uses the spec bins and put's all other countries in the RO Region bin ---------------------------

result2_SubCloud = group result_SubCloud by ('Region_Level2', 'Country');
result2_SubCloud = foreach result2_SubCloud generate 'Region_Level2' as 'Region_Level2', 
case when ('Region_Level2' == "AMER" && ('Country' ==  "Canada" ))then "Canada" when ('Region_Level2' == "AMER" && ('Country' ==  "United States" ))then "United States" when ('Region_Level2' == "AMER")then "RO AMER" when  ('Region_Level2' == "EMEA" && ('Country' ==  "United Kingdom" ))then "United Kingdom"  when  ('Region_Level2' == "EMEA" && ('Country' ==  "France" ))then "France" when  ('Region_Level2' == "EMEA" && ('Country' ==  "Germany" ))then "Germany" when  ('Region_Level2' == "EMEA" && ('Country' ==  "Netherlands" ))then "Netherlands" when ('Region_Level2' == "EMEA" ) then "RO EMEA" when  ('Region_Level2' == "APAC" && ('Country' ==  "Australia" ))then "ANZ" when  ('Region_Level2' == "APAC" && ('Country' ==  "ANZ" ))then "ANZ"  when  ('Region_Level2' == "APAC" && ('Country' ==  "India" ))then "India"  when  ('Region_Level2' == "APAC" )then "RO APAC"  when  ('Region_Level2' == "APAC" )then "RO APAC"  when  ('Region_Level2' == "JP" && ('Country' ==  "Japan" ))then "Japan" when  ('Region_Level2' == "JP" && ('Country' ==  "South Korea" ))then "South Korea" when  ('Region_Level2' == "JP"  )then "RO JP"  when  ('Region_Level2' == "LACA" && ('Country' ==  "Brazil" ))then "Brazil" when ('Region_Level2' == "LACA" )then "RO LACA" else "ERROR" end as 'Country', 

coalesce(sum('{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} ACV Absolute'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} ACV Absolute',
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD ACV Absolute'), 0) as 'YTD ACV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} ACV Growth'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} ACV Growth',
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD ACV Growth'), 0) as 'YTD ACV Growth', 

coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Red_Accounts Absolute'), 0)  as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Red_Accounts Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD Red_Accounts Absolute'), 0)  as 'YTD Red_Accounts Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Red_Accounts Growth'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Red_Accounts Growth', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD Red_Accounts Growth'), 0) as 'YTD Red_Accounts Growth',

coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM Absolute'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD CSM Absolute'), 0) as 'YTD CSM Absolute',  
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM CAGR'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM CAGR',  
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD CSM CAGR'), 0) as 'YTD CSM CAGR', 

coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM Absolute'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD PSM Absolute'), 0) as 'YTD PSM Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM CAGR'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM CAGR', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD PSM CAGR'), 0) as 'YTD PSM CAGR';

------------------------------------------------------GROUPING FOR Mapped Countries ----------------------------
result2_SubCloud = group result2_SubCloud by ('Region_Level2', 'Country') left, MasterHierarchy by ('Level_1', 'Level_2');
result2_SubCloud = foreach result2_SubCloud generate result2_SubCloud.'Region_Level2' as 'Region_Level2', 
"  " + (result2_SubCloud.'Country') as 'Region', 

coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} ACV Absolute'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} ACV Absolute',
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD ACV Absolute'), 0) as 'YTD ACV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} ACV Growth'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} ACV Growth',
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD ACV Growth'), 0) as 'YTD ACV Growth', 

coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Red_Accounts Absolute'), 0)  as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Red_Accounts Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD Red_Accounts Absolute'), 0)  as 'YTD Red_Accounts Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Red_Accounts Growth'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Red_Accounts Growth', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD Red_Accounts Growth'), 0) as 'YTD Red_Accounts Growth', 

coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM Absolute'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD CSM Absolute'), 0) as 'YTD CSM Absolute',  
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM CAGR'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM CAGR',  
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD CSM CAGR'), 0) as 'YTD CSM CAGR', 

coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM Absolute'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD PSM Absolute'), 0) as 'YTD PSM Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM CAGR'), 0) as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM CAGR', 
coalesce(sum(result2_SubCloud.'YTD PSM CAGR'), 0) as 'YTD PSM CAGR',

last(MasterHierarchy.'Level_2_Sort_Code') as 'Sort_Code';


-------------------------------------UNION------------------------------
Final = union result, result2_SubCloud;

---------------------------------------FINAL PROJECTION --------------------------
Final = filter Final by 'Sort_Code' != "";
Final = order Final by ('Sort_Code' asc,  '{{cell(Cloud_Filter_1.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' asc);

Final = foreach Final generate 
'Region'+"" as 'Region', 

'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM Absolute' as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM',
'YTD CSM Absolute' as 'YTD CSM Absolute',
'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM CAGR' as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} CSM CAGR',
'YTD CSM CAGR' as 'YTD CSM CAGR' ,

'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM Absolute' as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM',
'YTD PSM Absolute' as 'YTD PSM Absolute',
'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM CAGR' as '{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} PSM CAGR',
'YTD PSM CAGR' as 'YTD PSM CAGR' , 

'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Red_Accounts Absolute', 
'YTD Red_Accounts Absolute',
'{{cell(Quarter_1.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Red_Accounts Growth',
'YTD Red_Accounts Growth' ;
